      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON. ¶ T. M. Curl, ¶  M. D., Manuha Bush-Station, Central Rangitikei, Wellington, New Zealand ¶ a gentleman attached to the study of ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.01.00b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates, 1877-82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">T. M. Curl,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The name is an error for 'S. M. Curl': see membership list <seg style="font-style: italic; ">in Transactions and Proceedings of the New Zealand Institute</seg>, vol. 9, 1876, p. li. A series of articles in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Transactions </seg>is similarly signed.</p>
               </note> M. D., Manuha Bush-Station, Central Rangitikei, Wellington, New Zealand</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History especially</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> </seg>applied Botany</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">being desirous of becoming a Fellow of the LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON, we, whose names are underwritten, beg leave to recommend him to that honour</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.8417in; text-align: center; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller M.D. F.L.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.8417in; text-align: center; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">William Woolls Ph.D, F.L.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.8417in; text-align: center; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Robt D Fitzgerald, F.L.S<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Curl's details completed and form signed by M; other supporters' autograph signatures. It is not known when M prepared the form or when it was signed by Woolls and Fitzgerald, but it was presumably early in 1879, and the item is numbered accordingly.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">This recommendation must be signed by Three or more Fellows.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.B. – The Christian name of the Candidate must be stated at length, as well as his Residence, and any special qualifications he may possess.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society, on the </seg>20th <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> March 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">The Ballot will take place on the </seg>17th <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> April 1879<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated on back</seg>: Dr. T. M Curl | Electd April 17, 1878.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
